{"tid":1831784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浸大舍堂有中國學生感染肺炎 現仍住宿","createTime":"2020-01-20T15:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T17:26:47.000Z","uid":70063,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3600e56481a768fa9116701c4076f5e39a227f","tid":1831784,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"據學生會幹事會內務副幹事長林穎澤指，本科生舍堂北座15樓有一名中國學生報稱於日前在深圳求醫後確診肺炎，雖未確認是否為武漢肺炎，但仍居留於宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n學生會隨後通報學生事務處及舍堂組，周樹人堂舍堂主任陳嘉榮稱現正跟進情況，並拒絕透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n該名染病學生現跟隨Non-local mentor到本校保健中心進行新型冠狀病毒的快速測試。<br />\n<br />\n本會呼籲同學注意個人衛生，出門時佩戴口罩，減低被傳染及患病的機會。本會將繼續關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/busueb/photos/a.426369960780538/2611817758902403/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbusueb%2Fphotos%2Fa.426369960780538%2F2611817758902403%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV98yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=19d54af7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/busueb/photos/a.426369960780538/2611817758902403/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e652cd0423180f14772e507ae2c1daa3496e3749","tid":1831784,"uid":332635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005ec42c8f7702deea77f52ce76a9c4c0bc5b257","tid":1831784,"uid":153781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"趕佢走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb50d0be301302f35d1151d3bd355fa7a6becf58","tid":1831784,"uid":101307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"重住hall既人真係自求多福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日防夜防 陣間啲大陸人一個咳痴就攪掂全層既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89c23a4138eaa2ce9d549748dfc104916eed939","tid":1831784,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike